KG name: Open Data Web - a CKAN based linked open data repository in Taiwan
Description: ==========================================================## Highlight 1: An old record is not a data but now defined as a new semantic dataset. * i.e. its triples- graphs- links- file formats ... * i.e. its revised- vocabulary encoded versions ... * ex. data:d2148340 a dcat:dataset. #files:json-ld- ttl- XML## Highlight 2: A new method to curate- publish & visualize LOD graphs via CKAN portal. * i.e. two models for one dataset published in two views. * ex. data:d2148340. # Dublin Core @schema1 * ex. data:d2148340 a data:Refined. # more semantics@schema2## Highlight 3: Validation & Reproducibility: Provenance and Contexts are in details. * Currently records from 74 agents who have roles in NGO (2)- Museum (5)- Library (2)- Government (9)- Archive (1)- and Academia (55).# Total Resources:* 843-309 records from 14 datasets.* 44-806-400 triples from 14 datasets encoded with DC 15 elements.* 25-913-304 triples from 832-803 records semantically refined with domain knowledges.
Authors: Name: Institute of Information Science; Academia Sinica; Email:andreahg@iis.sinica.edu.tw
Sources: Web:http://data.odw.tw/ Name:Andrea Wei-Ching Huang; Cheng-Jen Lee and Tyng-Ruey Chuang Email:andreahg@iis.sinica.edu.tw
